---Economics---
25 years project lifetime
Discount Rate: 6% (επιτόκιο αναγωγής)
OnM (Operation and Maintanance) cost: 1% of initial cost (ράντα - χρησιμοποίηση και δημιουργία αντίστοιχου γραφήματος)

Calculate battery lifetime by it's cycles
Include the cost of a new battery pack (i.e. at the 14th year)

Wind Turbine: 1,200,000.00€/MW
PV: 1,000,000.00€/MW

Lead-Carbon: 300,000.00€/MWh (~13.5-15 years lifetime for 5000cycles)
Lithium-Ion: 500,000.00€/MWh
